      <title>叙利亚临时总统首次出访沙特阿拉伯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/syria-s-interim-president-in-saudi-arabia-on-first-foreign-trip</link>
      <description><![CDATA[叙利亚临时总统艾哈迈德·沙拉周日抵达利雅得，开始他的首次正式出访，预计他将会见沙特王储穆罕默德·本·萨勒曼。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/syria-s-interim-president-in-saudi-arabia-on-first-foreign-trip</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 10:23:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国国际开发署网站关闭，美国援助前景存疑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/usaid-website-goes-dark-with-future-of-us-assistance-in-doubt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于特朗普政府继续审查美国国际开发署的未来以及美国对外援助的总体发展方向，美国国际开发署网站上周末下线。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/usaid-website-goes-dark-with-future-of-us-assistance-in-doubt</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 09:24:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国总理称法国政府将于周一寻求预算通过</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/french-government-to-seek-budget-adoption-monday-premier-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总理弗朗索瓦·贝鲁在接受《星期日论坛报》采访时表示，法国政府将寻求在周一推动通过 2025 年预算，这使得法国议会分裂后，政府有可能面临不信任投票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/french-government-to-seek-budget-adoption-monday-premier-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 08:38:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度经济增长放缓，莫迪青睐中产阶级而非失业者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/modi-favors-middle-class-over-jobless-as-india-s-growth-stumbles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为了缓解全球经济面临的不利影响，印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪在预算中为印度中产阶级提供了大幅减税，但几乎没有为去年投票反对他的数百万失业者提供直接支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/modi-favors-middle-class-over-jobless-as-india-s-growth-stumbles</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 05:27:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税瞄准中国网络零售商利用的漏洞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/trump-tariffs-target-loophole-used-by-chinese-online-retailers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统对中国、加拿大和墨西哥征收的新贸易税包括对电子商务的猛烈攻击，显然是计划取消长期以来对价值低于 800 美元的包裹的关税豁免。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/trump-tariffs-target-loophole-used-by-chinese-online-retailers</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 04:15:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国誓言对美国关税采取措施，威胁对世贸组织采取行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/china-vows-measures-to-counter-us-tariffs-threatens-wto-action</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普宣布对来自世界第二大经济体的进口产品征收 10% 的关税后，中国誓言对美国进行报复，但没有征收关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/china-vows-measures-to-counter-us-tariffs-threatens-wto-action</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 03:18:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>“彻底背叛”：特朗普关税举措扰乱重要贸易关系 加拿大陷入困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/-complete-betrayal-canada-reels-as-trump-tariff-hits-major-trade-relationship</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普签署行政命令，对几乎所有美国从加拿大进口的商品征收 25% 的关税，对能源产品征收 10% 的关税。此后，加拿大做好了应对经济动荡的准备，并制定了报复计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/-complete-betrayal-canada-reels-as-trump-tariff-hits-major-trade-relationship</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 01:35:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥承诺对美国征收关税，同时呼吁合作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/mexico-pledges-retaliatory-tariffs-against-us-while-calling-for-cooperation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥总统克劳迪娅·希恩鲍姆 (Claudia Sheinbaum) 准备对美国征收反关税，此前美国总统唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 承诺对墨西哥征收 25% 的关税，此举可能导致墨西哥经济陷入衰退。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/mexico-pledges-retaliatory-tariffs-against-us-while-calling-for-cooperation</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 01:16:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大、墨西哥回击特朗普关税，中国誓言采取行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/trump-hits-china-canada-mexico-with-tariffs-to-open-trade-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普兑现对加拿大和墨西哥进口商品征收 25% 关税的威胁后，加拿大和墨西哥誓言对美国进行反击，引发了一场势将重塑全球供应链的贸易战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/trump-hits-china-canada-mexico-with-tariffs-to-open-trade-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Feb 2025 22:06:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯用导弹轰炸乌克兰；库尔斯克学校遭袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/war-in-ukraine-six-killed-as-russia-renews-its-missile-bombardment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰当局称，周六俄罗斯使用导弹、无人机和航空炸弹对乌克兰进行猛烈轰炸，造成至少 6 人死亡，数人受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/war-in-ukraine-six-killed-as-russia-renews-its-missile-bombardment</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Feb 2025 09:35:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
